log into mpa, then
login to prelude via: ssh -XY prelude

change to your directory
cd /scratch/baumann

use screen to detach processes from main shell, so that they continue when you log off:
screen

to detach screen press ctrl+a+d

to resume screen: screen -r
if there are multiple screens, screen -r will give you IDs like this:
9337.pts-22.prelude	(Detached)
9318.pts-22.prelude	(Detached)

in that case resume via: screen -r 9337

to terminate screen, go into screen and then type: exit



